  <h2>About Us</h2>
  <br>
  <p>
    Bike Rental Thamel is your go-to destination for affordable and reliable 
    bike rentals in the heart of Kathmandu. Whether you're exploring the busy 
    streets of Thamel or heading out on an adventure, we have the perfect bike for you.
  </p>
  <br>
  <p>
    We offer a wide range of bikes including city bikes, mountain bikes, and 
    electric bikes — all well-maintained and ready to ride.
  </p>
  <br>
    <h3>Why Choose Us?</h3>
    <br>
  <p>
    We believe that the best way to experience Kathmandu is on two wheels. Our fleet 
    of bikes is regularly serviced and maintained to ensure your safety and comfort. 
    From narrow alleys of Thamel to the open roads leading to Nagarkot or Bhaktapur, 
    our bikes are built to handle it all.
  </p>
  <p>
    We offer flexible rental plans — hourly, daily, and weekly — so you can explore 
    at your own pace without breaking the bank. Our friendly staff is always ready to 
    help you pick the right bike and suggest the best routes around the valley.
  </p>
<br>
  <h3>Our Fleet</h3>
  <br>
  <p>
    We offer a wide range of bikes to suit every rider and every road:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>City Bikes — perfect for casual rides around Thamel and Kathmandu</li>
    <li>Mountain Bikes — ideal for off-road trails and hilly terrain</li>
    <li>Electric Bikes — eco-friendly and great for longer distances</li>
    <li>Kids Bikes — safe and fun for the little explorers</li>
  </ul>
<br>
  <h3>Our Commitment</h3>
  <br>
  <p>
    At Bike Rental Thamel, customer satisfaction is our top priority. We are committed 
    to providing clean, well-maintained bikes at the best prices. We also promote 
    sustainable and eco-friendly travel, encouraging more people to choose bikes over 
    motorized vehicles for short trips around the city.
  </p>
  <p>
    Come visit us at Thamel, Kathmandu — we are open 7 days a week and ready to 
    help you start your next adventure!
  </p>
